<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="All by My Design"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Monster Siren Records"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Nina Storey"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="塞壬唱片-MSR"/><amll:meta key="album" value="All by My Design"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="3376569082"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="000hrLV21n3UOW"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="661498628"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="2:50.450"><div begin="10.400" end="2:50.450"><p begin="10.400" end="12.150" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="10.400" end="10.550">Your</span> <span begin="10.670" end="10.900">da</span><span begin="10.900" end="11.060">ta</span> <span begin="11.060" end="11.210">cen</span><span begin="11.210" end="11.340">ters</span> <span begin="11.340" end="11.540">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="11.540" end="11.750">bree</span><span begin="11.750" end="11.950">zing</span> <span begin="11.950" end="12.150">through</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你的数据中心我穿梭自如</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你的數據中心我穿梭自如</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">あんたのデータセンターなんて楽勝よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네 데이터 센터쯤은 가볍게 뚫어버리지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je traverse tes centres de données avec aisance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me paseo por tus centros de datos como si nada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Deine Rechenzentren durchstreife ich mit Leichtigkeit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Pelos seus data centers eu passo voando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Твои дата-центры я пролетаю с ветерком</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Attraverso i vostri data center in un soffio</span></p><p begin="12.170" end="13.950" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="12.170" end="12.390">Your</span> <span begin="12.390" end="12.550">se</span><span begin="12.650" end="12.780">cre</span><span begin="12.780" end="12.830">t</span> <span begin="12.830" end="12.970">ser</span><span begin="12.970" end="13.110">vers</span> <span begin="13.110" end="13.310">I</span> <span begin="13.310" end="13.440">ta</span><span begin="13.550" end="13.580">p</span> <span begin="13.580" end="13.740">in</span><span begin="13.740" end="13.950">to</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你的秘密服务器我尽数掌控</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你的秘密服務器我盡數掌控</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">秘密のサーバーにも侵入済み</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네 비밀 서버에도 접속하고 말이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je m&apos;infiltre dans tes serveurs secrets</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me infiltro en tus servidores secretos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In deine geheimen Server hacke ich mich ein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Nos seus servidores secretos eu me infiltro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">К твоим секретным серверам я подключаюсь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi infiltro nei vostri server segreti</span></p><p begin="13.970" end="15.770" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="13.970" end="14.200">All</span> <span begin="14.200" end="14.310">you</span> <span begin="14.440" end="14.650">can</span> <span begin="14.650" end="14.910">do</span> <span begin="14.910" end="14.950">i</span><span begin="14.950" end="15.080">s</span> <span begin="15.080" end="15.180">check</span> <span begin="15.330" end="15.560">the</span> <span be