n Schritt voraus</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu fico um passo à sua frente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я всегда на шаг впереди тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Rimango sempre un passo avanti a voi</span></p><p begin="17.760" end="18.430" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="17.760" end="17.960">Wa</span><span begin="17.960" end="18.010">tch</span> <span begin="18.010" end="18.110">it</span> <span begin="18.110" end="18.410">loa</span><span begin="18.410" end="18.430">d</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">看着它加载吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">看著它加載吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ロードを見つめて</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">로딩되는 걸 지켜봐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Regarde-le charger</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mira cómo carga</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sieh zu wie es lädt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Assista carregar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Смотри как грузится</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Guardalo caricare</span></p><p begin="18.660" end="20.220" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="18.660" end="18.800">Pa</span><span begin="18.800" end="18.840">tch</span> <span begin="18.840" end="18.900">up</span> <span begin="19.030" end="19.120">the</span> <span begin="19.120" end="19.290">bug</span><span begin="19.290" end="19.370">s</span> <span begin="19.370" end="19.570">re</span><span begin="19.570" end="19.670">write</span> <span begin="19.770" end="19.880">the</span> <span begin="19.880" end="20.220">code</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">修复漏洞 重写代码</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">修復漏洞 重寫代碼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">バグにパッチを当ててコードを書き換える</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">버그를 패치하고 코드를 다시 써</spa